All observers/participants MUST remain seated at all times when not called to fight.  This means NO running around DM chair, gong, etc., casting spells, etc.  Failure to observe this rule will get you sent to HELL for 5min.

When called to combat, you will enter the arena, NO BUFFS prior to match, however you may REST if needed.  The DM will then cast 2 dispell magics, and AFTER the 2nd dispell magic is done, FIGHT.  Also, after the 2 dispell magics, you may use ANY BUFFS you wish, this includes potions, spells, items, anything.  NO HEALING of any kind allowed.  Regeneration is allowed.

If you leave the arena, you are disqualified.  If you use any form of healing, you are disqualified.

The DM will ressurect anyone that dies.

All cheering, jeering, and talking is allowed, and most of all HAVE FUN!!!

These rules may be modified by the DM at anytime, the DM will notifiy you if there are any changes.
